    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - FULLER 10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS - INSPECT - SPLINED SHAFTS
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="inspect" graphiccount="0">
        <title>SPLINED SHAFTS</title>
        <para>Inspect splines for twisting, cracking, or wear. Replace splined shafts as necessary.</para>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Worn splines may indicate excessive torsional vibration. Make sure the vehicle system is corrected
                    to prevent recurring damage to the transmission.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
    </svcproc>
